Virtualenv:
	
	{path : /usr/bin/python3 /tmp/bootcamp}
	
	* for activating : . /tmp/bootcamp/bin/activate
	* for creating a venv : virtualenv -p /usr/bin/python3 <path>
	* for deactivating : deactivate while in venv
	* for removing : rm -rf <venv_name>
	
Setting up postgresql
	
PostgreSQL:

	* createdb <db_name> : create a database with name : db_name
	* psql <db_name> : connect to the database
	* /dt : for showing the database(postgresql command)
	* select <fields (with commas)> from <db_name> : prints the fields specified(* prints all)
	
	*export FLASK_ENV = development : all debugging is active in flask
